# 📊 Business Performance Dashboard - Power BI

## Overview
This project is an interactive Business Performance Dashboard created using Power BI. It helps analyze business performance by displaying important metrics and visualizations in a simple and interactive way.

## Dashboard Metrics
* Total Revenue
* Total Cost
* Total Profit
* Total Customers
* Total New Users
* Total Premium Users

## Dashboard Visualizations
* KPI cards showing key business metrics.
* Monthly Revenue Trend to analyze revenue performance over time.
* Comparison of New Users and Premium Users.
* Comparison of Total Cost and Total Profit.
* Month slicer to filter and analyze dashboard data for specific months.

## Tools Used
* Power BI
* Microsoft Excel

## Skills Demonstrated
* Data Cleaning
* Data Modeling
* Data Visualization
* Dashboard Design
* Interactive Report Development

## Key Insights
* Monitored monthly revenue trends.
* Compared business cost and profit.
* Tracked customer growth using new and premium user metrics.
* Used interactive filters for better business analysis.

